{"tid":214406,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉貼）日語配音同粵語配音比較，粵語版明顯佔上風","createTime":"2017-04-23T17:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T02:51:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6051769de89c82279ac639b0c756897aff51ba1","tid":214406,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"由於最近《進擊的巨人》第二輯的播映，前幾天又把第一季翻了出來再看一遍。<br />\n<br />\n因為以前沒有看過日語版，我做了個無聊的舉動，不斷地將不同的聲道切來換去，聽不同的演繹，總覺得日語版有什麼怪怪的，然後終於發現哪裡不妥了。<br />\n<br />\n以下為第一輯第14集部分節錄，花3分鐘聽聽，TVB版和日本版的分別。<br />\n<br />\n在空曠廣闊的議事法庭裡，粵語版裡角色說話的聲音都作了室內迴音反彈處理，反觀日語版並沒有此效果。<br />\n<br />\n然後是當鏡頭轉換時，粵語版的混錄會根據畫面的內容做出了相應的調整，把角色說話時的聲音分成大小、遠近、前後、左右，使得各人的聲音有距離感和方向性，令整套作品的音效昇華。相反日語版除非出現疊聲，不然個各人說話的音量都是一樣的，就像都站在同一點讀對白。<br />\n<br />\n雖然只是小小調整，但此舉卻把整個配音作品的質量昇華去到製作的級數。這個帖並非要質疑日本版的質量，而是在外面一些人嚷著「原聲比配音好」的大潮流下，如此狹窄的市場裡，能夠堅持認真製作，實在是廣大觀眾之福！希望TVB的配音組繼續擇善固執的精神，因為你們付出的努力是有人看到的<br />\n<br />\n抱歉，好像寫得太長了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/5817798250/permalink/10154637976223251/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F5817798250%2Fpermalink%2F10154637976223251%2F&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6KEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=cf5dcfc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/5817798250/permalink/10154637976223251/</a>"},{"pid":"c1fce8e2da69730dbb787cdb529eddd7640c1154","tid":214406,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T18:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62b0a76afeac206221f9abe13ea33fd222e8e6e","tid":214406,"uid":10001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T18:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94d1b739ebceb573489eabc1867dd3ddef909ee","tid":214406,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T18:47:23.000Z","msg":"質量? 對話多咗?"},{"pid":"5b6e8f695034d92702fabb08624d3562e8f2061b","tid":214406,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T20:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>質量? 對話多咗?</blockquote><br />\n應該會重咗"},{"pid":"252eb6df767592da60ef3b6f857cf493746ebf50","tid":214406,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>質量? 對話多咗?</blockquote><br />\n應該會重咗</blockquote><br />\n即係啲sound wave pressure大咗? 明明 surface area 大咗喎... 定 係recorded fidelity個distribution?"},{"pid":"b2d652ff23ab80d63dfd1be86d38fef5ceebd4c0","tid":214406,"uid":93937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:32:15.000Z","msg":"日文版迴音有少少？<br />\n<br />\n唔知制作流程趕唔趕，巨人出碟時畫都執過，記得有人整左好多對比圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過冇人講聲，可能出碟都冇執返靚"},{"pid":"f3eddc14b36e1819845c0b437588385aa8398004","tid":214406,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8482c223fd1f63ae0b8ea1564dced69a07bf398","tid":214406,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f2dc4e281b01e8face8cfb580cbdf0b5a3042e","tid":214406,"uid":34264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"其實講捉口<br />\n香港班配音員準過日本個啲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講神韻亦唔輸蝕<br />\n粵配版鋼鍊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96161023e59846a33ba2b10984cdd15a0d3886cb","tid":214406,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實講捉口<br />\n香港班配音員準過日本個啲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講神韻亦唔輸蝕<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">粵配版鋼鍊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997cbf22c486bf3ffc11c1f2fa3a488d96fedc79","tid":214406,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:03:01.000Z","msg":"tbb粵配正好多<br />\n日文配音 女角色 句句配到淫叫咁嘅聲<br />\n聽到好尷尬"},{"pid":"295c421259e0f61bec3b5150138eb7ae2e12901a","tid":214406,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:06:47.000Z","msg":"廣東話版花師奶係世界級"},{"pid":"5d8eada988dabde8773a8427977d99790f2a1edc","tid":214406,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"衝鋒21<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蛭魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8d6ff6e628a512d32716e99c4fbac590f7df5c","tid":214406,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>tbb粵配正好多<br />\n日文配音 女角色 句句配到淫叫咁嘅聲<br />\n聽到好尷尬</blockquote><br />\n細個睇慣百變小櫻粵配版，有次係朋友屋企睇日本原音版，聽到知世把聲變咗蚊滋咁又尖又細，勁唔慣。不過知世係小學生，都算係配合角色。<br />\n<br />\n新世紀福音戰士無論日文原音，定粵配(VCD版)都真係世界級。"},{"pid":"e73fa7627d097c4d737d0fb73d3155c221fc3244","tid":214406,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>tbb粵配正好多<br />\n日文配音 女角色 句句配到淫叫咁嘅聲<br />\n聽到好尷尬</blockquote><br />\n細個睇慣百變小櫻粵配版，有次係朋友屋企睇日本原音版，聽到知世把聲變咗蚊滋咁又尖又細，勁唔慣。不過知世係小學生，都算係配合角色。<br />\n<br />\n新世紀福音戰士無論日文原音，定粵配(VCD版)都真係世界級。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聲線呢家嘢係先入為主啫<br />\n正如我地聽慣我們這一家嘅粵配版入面花師奶好似阿嬸嗰把聲，再聽日文就會日配把聲好古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但人地都可能掉返轉諗我地把聲先怪，因為花師奶個設定好似得42歲 <br />\n<br />\n不過TVB嘅配音真係幾認真<br />\n有時睇啲外購台灣旅遊節目，TVB係幫埋唔係講國語嘅當地人配埋廣東話<br />\n不過就搞到同一樣嘢用廣東話重覆講兩次"},{"pid":"801144fa8e959a0d1f59d8f5fc423c574f0268db","tid":214406,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>tbb粵配正好多<br />\n日文配音 女角色 句句配到淫叫咁嘅聲<br />\n聽到好尷尬</blockquote><br />\n唔淫邊到正"},{"pid":"64603dbe6e02d0935438da496a14082b7f7ee911","tid":214406,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}